item.title: CVE-2021-21552|2024-08-03T18:16:22.986Z -- dell -- wyse%20windows%20embedded%20%28wes%29
item.description: Dell Wyse Windows Embedded System versions WIE10 LTSC 2019 and earlier contain an improper authorization vulnerability. A local authenticated malicious user with low privileges may potentially exploit this vulnerability to bypass the restricted environment and perform unauthorized actions on the affected system.
